This software has the following third-party dependencies. They are fetched at
build time (see scripts/setup-mbedtls.sh) and are NOT redistributed in this
repository; their own license terms apply to the fetched copies:

  * Mbed TLS — Apache-2.0
    https://github.com/Mbed-TLS/mbedtls
    The PowerPC / Classic Mac OS target links a classic-Mac fork of Mbed TLS
    (TLS-client configuration + mbedtls_hardware_poll entropy), by cy384.

  * Retro68 cross-compiler toolchain (build dependency only)
    https://github.com/autc04/Retro68

This software includes data derived from a public specification:

  * The HPACK static table (src/cn_hpack_tables.h) is derived from
    RFC 7541, Appendix A (HPACK: Header Compression for HTTP/2).
